sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Form as artist-form /<br/>BioGenerationSection
    participant Hook as useGenerateArtistBioMutation
    participant Action as generateArtistBioAction<br/>(Server Action)
    participant Svc as BioGenerationService
    participant Lambda as fakefour-bio-generator<br/>(or fixture)
    participant Img as BioImageService
    participant S3 as S3 / CDN
    participant Repo as ArtistRepository
    participant DB as MongoDB

    Admin->>Form: Enter links + description, click "Generate bios"
    Form->>Hook: mutateAsync({ artistId, links?, description? })
    Hook->>Action: generateArtistBioAction(input)
    Action->>Action: requireRole('admin') + validate (Zod)
    Action->>Svc: generateForArtist(artistId, opts)
    Svc->>Repo: findById(artistId)
    Repo->>DB: read artist (names, genres)
    Svc->>Lambda: invoke (InvokeCommand) /<br/>fakeBioGeneration if BIO_GENERATOR_FAKE
    Note over Lambda: MusicBrainz → Wikidata →<br/>Wikimedia → Groq prose
    Lambda-->>Svc: { ok, data: {shortBio,longBio,genres,images,links,model} }
    Svc->>Svc: sanitizeBioHtml / sanitizeBioText
    loop each discovered image
        Svc->>Img: rehostWithVariants(url, artistId, i)
        Img->>S3: upload original + _w variants (sharp/WebP)
        S3-->>Img: CDN url + dims
    end
    Svc->>Repo: replaceBioContent(artistId, content)
    Repo->>DB: tx: delete old images/links,<br/>update Artist, create new rows
    Svc-->>Action: { ok, data, slug }
    Action->>Action: logSecurityEvent + revalidatePath(*)
    Action-->>Hook: { success:true, data: GeneratedBioContent }
    Hook->>Hook: invalidateQueries(artists.all)
    Hook-->>Form: onGenerated(content) → populate RichTextEditor fields
    Admin->>Form: Edit + Save
